but we all ran into different kinds of trouble on the way,

00:17:01.230 --> 00:17:02.710
so we must have missed something during that.

00:17:04.070 --> 00:17:04.550
For example,

00:17:07.360 --> 00:17:08.990
what kind of person do you think would kill someone?

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:10.840
Anyone

00:17:11.470 --> 00:17:12.470
could do that.

