That's the problem.

00:17:15.840 --> 00:17:17.200
We all thought that anyone

00:17:17.680 --> 00:17:18.920
who could commit such a big crime

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:20.270
must not be an ordinary person,

00:17:21.550 --> 00:17:22.790
but we were wrong.

