I checked your ledgers.

00:18:54.960 --> 00:18:56.880
That gold frame glass mirror

00:18:57.440 --> 00:18:58.960
only cost you 800 coins,

00:18:59.750 --> 00:19:01.120
which isn't even enough for a goat.

00:19:02.440 --> 00:19:05.030
The merchant, however desperate for money,

00:19:05.750 --> 00:19:07.120
could not have sold it for so little.

00:19:13.750 --> 00:19:15.200
I'll say. I'll say it all.

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:16.640
Those things

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:17.990
are stolen.

00:19:18.840 --> 00:19:20.550
Everyone in Xichuan has different skills.

