Is a piece of stolen property

00:19:22.180 --> 00:19:23.120
worth hiding?

00:19:24.030 --> 00:19:26.400
How could someone making Night Owl do this

00:19:26.600 --> 00:19:28.600
be an ordinary person?

00:19:29.160 --> 00:19:30.680
I'm just afraid

00:19:30.830 --> 00:19:32.380
of getting in trouble.

