I can't say

00:38:27.070 --> 00:38:27.920
for sure right now.

00:38:30.590 --> 00:38:32.070
You don't need to tell me things

00:38:32.070 --> 00:38:33.550
you can't be sure of in the future.

00:38:34.670 --> 00:38:35.920
But I have another matter.

00:38:36.400 --> 00:38:36.710
Please.

