So the Chairman decided to make a countermeasure

00:39:03.070 --> 00:39:04.630
and took a group of men there,

00:39:04.880 --> 00:39:05.800
but they came up empty

00:39:07.190 --> 00:39:08.960
and fought with the reckless men for nothing.

00:39:09.360 --> 00:39:10.070
Where did the information come from?

00:39:10.670 --> 00:39:12.400
We have people around Ma Gang.

00:39:13.000 --> 00:39:14.680
A bunch of esnes?

00:39:18.960 --> 00:39:19.800
How do you know?

00:39:20.480 --> 00:39:21.920
If I'm right,

00:39:23.150 --> 00:39:24.750
