They're my neighbors

00:40:31.140 --> 00:40:32.730
and have watched me grow up.

00:40:33.000 --> 00:40:34.260
I couldn't hurt them.

00:40:34.260 --> 00:40:35.200
Useless kindness.

00:40:45.760 --> 00:40:47.250
For the greater good,

00:40:48.040 --> 00:40:48.980
we sometimes just have to

00:40:48.980 --> 00:40:50.520
